Get-CimInstance Win32_PhysicalMemory
    - Lists installed RAM modules, speed, size, and manufacturer.

Get-CimInstance Win32_Processor
    - Displays CPU model, cores, logical processors, and speed.

Get-Volume
    - Shows all volumes with drive letters, labels, file systems, and free space.

Get-PSDrive
    - Lists all PowerShell drives including local disks and mapped locations.
